# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added

- Keep track of reactions on messages posted in the curation channel
- Undo reactions that were added by authors to their own posts
- Post messages that reach a certain reaction threshold to curation gems channel
- In a database, keep track of which messages have been curated
- Synchronizes post between the curation and curation gems channel
    - If a post has been shared in the curation gems channel, and the original gets updated, the shared one will also be updated